profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
We have been providing our construction services for almost 15 years helping our clients to renovate and enhance their living space. Novacon Construction Inc are a full DESIGN-BUILD firm focusing on large scale higher end Major renovations, Home additions and full Custom Homes. We are a very well planned company that work well with clients that are looking for a high end/professional building experience and not a jack of all trades approach. Our clients work with a professional DESIGN-BUILD team that consists of in house designer, Project manager, Site supervisor and tradesman for the duration of their build.
 
Our aim is to produce a high quality product, to perform in the most efficient way possible, and to make your renovation a positive and rewarding experience. All our trades people are highly skilled and bring with them a wealth of experience. NOVACON Custom Builders & Renovators are equipped to work on any area of your home, from major additions, basements, to bathrooms, including kitchen development and we can even build your dream home!
 
A satisfied customer is our best advertisement!!!.

profile:
Getting started can sometimes be a daunting task to any homeowner. That’s where our Design/Build expertise can help simplify things. Once we have a basic understanding of what you are trying to achieve, we can design and build a space that perfectly meets your requirements.

At Elite Construction and Renovations, our clients needs come first. Upon your initial meeting, you’ll know you’re working with a company that cares about your project as much as you do. We promise to work with our clients to help them fulfill their vision of their dream home.
services:
INFILLS - Build a brand new home on an existing lot. Revive your home and add value to your property.

ADDITIONS - Add more living space to your existing home. Our home additions are designed to give you the extra space you need to live comfortably.

RENOVATIONS - Transform your existing living space and make your dreams a reality.

UNDERPINS - Increase basement ceiling height to achieve new living space.
specialities:
What separates us from our competitors is our ability to build our custom homes in 6 months or less without compromising quality. This is achieved by our team of highly experienced professionals who work with you from initial conception to construction completion and ensure your project is completed within your budget.
It is our guarantee that if we exceed 6 months to build your custom home, we will reimburse you of any temporary living expenses you may incur.

profile:
4168455052 - STRUCTURAL ENGINEERING - DESIGN - BUILD - RENOVATION  - Estezo Estates is a Family Company that designs and builds strong, safe, highly energy efficient, green, LEED compliant custom homes in the Greater Toronto Area. Originally a Father-son business, Estezo Estates started out as a renovations company. Orlando, who has an engineering background, and his son Jerson who has extensive design experience, started a renovations company in 2007 and it quickly turned into a full service construction company with its very own in house design department. Whether your looking for structural engineering, a design/permit, a renovation/construction service or all of the above Estezo Estates is right choice! We have combined the theory of design with actual real life on site building experience, bridging the long standing gap between designers and builders all under one roof, Estezo Estates.

We also project manage high end construction projects and remodels.

CONSTRUCTION

profile:
"My Prestigious Home" is where you need to be...

MPH has been a leader in major renovations and custom home construction since 2007. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project and better to say, your investment. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, MPH is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our vast professional experience, skilled expertise and attention to details enable us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way.
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.

We understand custom homes and renovations are amongst the most important investment to people in their lifetime. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that MPH is most definitely the qualified team for your project.

We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally hundreds of renovations since our inception. 

Please view our website at http://MyPrestigiousHome.com to view images of some of our projects.

Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship.

With 2 year Warranty, we at MPH know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients.

Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

MPH is an innovative, full service design/build/construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There are many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands.

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones.

Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free. Remember, we are talking about Professional Advice from Skilled Engineer.
Our areas of servings are in Toronto, Beaches, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Richmond hill, Markham, Foresthill, Royal York, Vaughan, Woodbridge, East York, West end, Central Toronto, North York, & Downtown Toronto.

services:
At any scale, TC Homes presents each client with superior service and attention throughout the project. 

Services include:

new construction 
renovation/tenant improvements 
project management 
construction management 
bobcat excavation
estimating and scheduling 
in-house services 
renovations 
From beginning to end, effective construction management is essential to any project. The Project Manager coordinates all aspects of the project and is the primary contact for all needs and concerns for the duration of the project. TC Homes has a commitment to the project and team and employs pre-construction value engineering, savings through negotiated projects, and project-specific construction strategy, while presenting and maintaining the construction schedule with expert project coordination.
The In-House Service Division provides TC Homes clients with continued service after construction is complete. This includes:

facilities management 
monthly or yearly inspections 
cost analysis for budgets 
hourly rates for in-house work 
third party negotiations for other services 
24-hour emergency service 
commercial painting 
exotic coatings

Welcome to Mattamy Homes: One product, lovingly crafted, humbly sold, then proudly owned. That's how it starts for most companies. That's how it started for Mattamy Homes in 1978.

Mattamy Homes is the largest privately owned homebuilder in North America, with a nearly 40-year history of operations across the United States and Canada. We are a custom home builder expert based in Toronto. We are known for various home improvement and construction services we have done since its establishment in 2004.

We operate on a design-build plan of action, in which the same team who designs the project construct it as well. 

As a method of work, we highlight single-point-responsibility through the design-build action plan. The same subcontracting team who designs the project constructs it, reduces project costs, and enables us to deliver on time.

We do best in custom home carpentry framing, custom home building, house construction demolition, and house renovations. We also cater to roof replacement projects, basement renovation, house extension, flooring repair, and room makeover.

profile:
Zamani Homes have been building Toronto’s most distinctive custom homes for over two decades. Founded in 1979 by Mohsen Zamani, the company has developed a reputation as one of the city’s leading boutique builders, catering to clients in the city’s most exclusive neighbourhoods, including the Bridle Path, Forest Hill, York Mills and Bayview.
 
Zamani came to Canada with extensive international building experience; after studying Engineering in Europe, he built luxury custom homes for well-heeled clients across Europe and the Middle East. He is known worldwide for his attention to detail and his commitment to unparalleled quality and customer service. Today, Zamani Homes is one the largest builders of custom homes in the GTA, building up to ten luxury homes per year ranging from 4,000 – 12,000 square feet.
 
Flora Zamani, a partner in the business, contributes the tremendous design expertise and attention to detail that the Zamani’s are known for. Lorraine Park in North York and the upcoming Eagle Heights development in Newmarket offer Zamani’s remarkable quality – at a price that’s more accessible to the average home buyer.
 
The Zamani family is a remarkable team focused on providing every homeowner – from custom-build clients to townhome buyers, with extraordinary quality, excellent service, eco-friendly materials, and above all, a beautiful, comfortable place they can be proud to call home.
name: Zamani Homes Ltd

profile:
Empire Communities is one of Canada's largest integrated master-planned community home builders. Over the past 20+ years, we have built more than 10,000 new homes and condominiums in some of the most sought-after locations in the GTA and Southwest Ontario. Our diverse portfolio includes neighbourhoods of beautiful homes, as well as towering skyscrapers that are landmarks of urban sophistication. 

As one of Canada's leading developers it is natural that Empire would look to the United States for land development and home building opportunities. With over 1,000 acres and 4,000 homesites under development in the U.S. market, Empire's experienced team is poised for growth and success.

Imaginative planning. Uncompromising standards. Attention to detail. Exceptional customer care. These are values that have shaped Empire Communities over the years. It’s these very values that win us the industry’s most prestigious awards year after year – and more importantly – the satisfaction and loyalty of our customers.
name: Empire Communities
